{"tid":2052014,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"曹永廉Po梁競徽撐國安法改圖相惹批評：我同佢事前有溝通！","createTime":"2020-06-05T07:57:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-05T08:09:28.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"bb5713db84afe15bd47669f7e818476a70ae0531","tid":2052014,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T07:57:23.000Z","msg":"早前曹永廉在其微博上載一張梁競徽手持一張文宣，上面寫有「支持立國安法，維持香港安定」的相片，事後被網民發現曹永廉上載的相片原來是P圖，其實梁競徽原圖是寫有：「向前線消防員致敬」，其後曹永廉遭到網民圍插企圖借梁競徽過橋表忠愛國。<br />\n<br />\n昨晚（4/6）曹永廉出席活動時接受《香港01》訪問，就此事回應說：「其實嗰張相我以前都有影過，幾年前有個消防員過身，我哋大家都有寫咗一啲慰問字句喺張卡度，而佢因為辣着咗好多火頭，啲人就幫佢啲字改晒，咁樣我覺得好唔公平，佢都有同我講佢都有啲唔開心。」（Po佢啲相前佢喺知道？）阿廉續說：「佢係知道， 我係有同佢溝通，其實我都唔想有咁多仇恨。」（話你借佢過橋？）「其實我冇嘅，我自己都唔需要做到咁，我哋大家都係好朋友嚟㗎，我哋都有聯絡，如果大家話我借機抽水，唔緊要嘅，我都冇所謂。」"},{"pid":"070a45f6444d29f67292e8054af0b299ee62df70","tid":2052014,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T07:57:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200605/345549598338715648.jpeg/_WBwnHLVXKu2PGfsASxMqewGLr7jQUWVUaq5YlGquWI?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200605%2F345549598338715648.jpeg%2F_WBwnHLVXKu2PGfsASxMqewGLr7jQUWVUaq5YlGquWI%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=6bd94bc2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"edda53c9c3c77cd588242554ed09dfcc24bb06ff","tid":2052014,"uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T07:58:47.000Z","msg":"辣殺曹永廉唔敢撐中國 點對得住祖國<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2794ff6dda6ce87c0ee7c0459fa6aa694624380","tid":2052014,"uid":212223,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T08:01:33.000Z","msg":"想屈手足撐國安法? 可恥呀"},{"pid":"fc3ec3d550a075113c4fe0d4ffa28c1f9315c531","tid":2052014,"uid":132587,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T08:02:03.000Z","msg":"連自己人都撚佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c17c4bb0fb2dea6cf5174f5b31512cb090ecc3c2","tid":2052014,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T08:06:21.000Z","msg":"曹永廉背棄左我地中國 嚴重損害13億中國人民的民族感情"},{"pid":"7490df31e956b0ce8bced03143fa3cca31c4d70e","tid":2052014,"uid":63311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T08:07:40.000Z","msg":"戴ny帽 唔愛國"},{"pid":"cc3350437f9ddfb8988bb045ac9e98f5568c57d7","tid":2052014,"uid":268519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T08:09:28.000Z","msg":"支持都仲有好多方法 乜咁大整蠱呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}